title: Living Well Welcomes Zach Washburn—Our New Movie Critic
text: Living Well Welcomes Zach Washburn--Our New Movie Critic By Clip Syndicate We are introducing a new segment on Living Well. We now have a resident Movie Critic, Zach Washburn. Zach is also the General Manager at Landmark Cinemas. He will be joining us each Thursday to let us know what's debuting at the theaters each week. Today, he told us all about Black Mass, Maze Runner, and Captive--movies opening tomorrow at Landmark Cinemas.
